data.message: Deployed 2 parallel agents to research design study materials and tools: Agent 1 compiled study materials covering: Glassmorphism, Bento Grids, Landing Pages, Color Theory, Typography from verified sources (Figma, Google, Apple, Smashing Magazine). Agent 2 compiled tools for: Gradient generators, Color palette tools, UI component libraries, Icon/illustration resources, CSS generators, Design system references. Both lists saved to Duro memory.
